                <note type="abstract">Contains a classification of manuscripts containing a Greek-based version of the
Prophets which the author attributes to a certain priest named al-ʿAlam. This version is used in the Paris and London Polyglots. Vaccari discusses the translator, time of composition as well as the date of the original Greek manuscript used as a Vorlage and offers reproductions from Isaiah 44 and
45.</note>
